      • NCLIENTS

        static final String NCLIENTS
        The #of concurrent clients to run. 20 is a reasonable value for testing concurrency. 1 means one reader or writer (you can decide which it will be using PERCENT_READERS.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • PERCENT_READERS

        static final String PERCENT_READERS
        The percentage of trials that are tasked as AbstractMRMWTestCase.ReaderTasks rather than AbstractMRMWTestCase.WriterTasks. Zero (0.0) means only writers. One (1.0) means only readers. .8d is a common mixure reflecting that there are typically more read operations than write operations.

        Note: There is NO validation of correctness unless you are running BOTH writers and readers!

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
